# Changelog

All major changes to bronko will be documented in this file

## [v0.0.3] - 10/28/2025
- Introduced baseline noise filter using streaming version of modified thompson tau filter 
- Now reporting statisticaly adjusted base counts and depths in pileup and vcf

## [v0.0.2] - 10/20/2025
- Fixed major bug when counting kmers for paired end reads 
- Introduced SOR strand filter replacement for previous naive method 

## [v0.0.1] - 10/16/2025
First public pre-release of bronko

### Added 
- bronko call
- bronko build